<BaseLayout title="Mockly — 0xdpslabs" description="Mock APIs and fake data for development and testing">
  <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); font-size: 0.875rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);">
    <a href="/">Home</a> / Mockly
  </p>

  <h1>Mockly</h1>
  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);">
    Free mock API service with 100+ resources for testing and development
  </p>

  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>
    A modern, schema-driven alternative to JSONPlaceholder. Free mock API service for testing and development
    with realistic data powered by gofakeit.
  </p>

  <h2>Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Schema-driven API - Add endpoints by creating JSON schemas (zero code)</li>
    <li>100+ resources across 14 categories</li>
    <li>Realistic data powered by gofakeit with 50+ generators</li>
    <li>CRUD-ready mock endpoints</li>
    <li>Filters and validation</li>
    <li>Response caching</li>
    <li>JSONPlaceholder / httpbin-style workflows</li>
    <li>No setup required</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Categories</h2>
  <p>Resources organized into logical groups including people, commerce, content, and more.</p>

  <h2>Status</h2>
  <p>Active development</p>

